<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Best Friend Contract</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f1eb 0%, #e8ddd4 100%);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .contract {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border: 2px solid #8B4513;
            position: relative;
            background-image: 
                repeating-linear-gradient(
                    transparent,
                    transparent 24px,
                    #e0e0e0 24px,
                    #e0e0e0 25px
                );
        }
        
        .contract::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 60px;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 2px;
            background: #ff6b6b;
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #8B4513;
            text-decoration: underline;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding-left: 20px;
            line-height: 28px;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .intro {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .terms {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .term {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 13px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        
        .term-number {
            min-width: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #8B4513;
        }
        
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
            border-top: 2px solid #8B4513;
            padding-top: 25px;
        }
        
        .signature-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .signature-box {
            width: 45%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .signature-line {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            height: 40px;
            position: relative;
            background: rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.1);
        }
        
        .signature-text {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        .date-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .date-line {
            display: inline-block;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
            width: 200px;
            height: 25px;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
        
        .thumb-impression {
            width: 60px;
            height: 80px;
            border: 2px solid #8B4513;
            border-radius: 30px;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, #d4a574 30%, #8B4513 70%);
            margin: 10px auto;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .thumb-impression::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: 
                repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 2px, rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.3) 2px, rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.3) 4px),
                repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, transparent, transparent 2px, rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.2) 2px, rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.2) 4px);
            border-radius: 30px;
        }
        
        .acknowledgment {
            background: rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px dashed #8B4513;
            margin-top: 25px;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 22px;
        }
        
        .heart {
            color: #ff6b6b;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .decorative-border {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            right: 10px;
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border: 2px solid #ff6b6b;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="contract">
        <div class="decorative-border">
            <span class="heart">â™¥</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="header">
            <div class="title">BEST FRIEND CONTRACT</div>
            <div class="subtitle">A Promise of Love, Trust & Friendship</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="intro">
                This contract is made with all my heart and soul, between me, <strong>Jissmon Joseph</strong>, and <strong>my babygirl, my soul Jyoti</strong>, who means the world to me. This is my promise to be the best friend, partner, and companion you could ever ask for.
            </div>
            
            <div class="terms">
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">1.</span>
                    <span>I promise to always be honest with you, even when the truth is difficult to share.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">2.</span>
                    <span>I will love you exactly as you are today and support you as you grow into who you want to become.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">3.</span>
                    <span>I promise to listen to you with my full attention, without judgment or the need to fix everything.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">4.</span>
                    <span>I will always make time for you, no matter how busy life gets.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">5.</span>
                    <span>I promise to be your biggest cheerleader and celebrate all your victories, big and small.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">6.</span>
                    <span>I will hold your hand through tough times and never let you face challenges alone.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">7.</span>
                    <span>I promise to remember important dates and make you feel special on ordinary days too.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">8.</span>
                    <span>I will respect your opinions, even when we disagree, and work together to find solutions.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">9.</span>
                    <span>I promise to keep your secrets safe and be someone you can trust completely.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">10.</span>
                    <span>I will surprise you with little gestures of love and kindness when you least expect it.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">11.</span>
                    <span>I promise to laugh with you, cry with you, and share in all of life's moments.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">12.</span>
                    <span>I will always choose "us" over "me" when making important decisions.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">13.</span>
                    <span>I promise to grow and learn from our mistakes together, never giving up on us.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">14.</span>
                    <span>I will support your dreams and ambitions, even if they take you far from me.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">15.</span>
                    <span>I promise to communicate openly and never let problems build up in silence.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">16.</span>
                    <span>I will appreciate the little things you do and never take your love for granted.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">17.</span>
                    <span>I promise to be patient with you, especially when you're having a difficult day.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">18.</span>
                    <span>I will create new adventures and memories with you, making our story beautiful.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">19.</span>
                    <span>I promise to remain the same loving, caring person you fell for, while growing better each day.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">20.</span>
                    <span>I will protect our relationship from negativity and always choose love over pride.</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="term">
                    <span class="term-number">21.</span>
                    <span>I promise that no matter what happens, you will always have a best friend in me.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="acknowledgment">
                <strong>ACKNOWLEDGMENT:</strong><br>
                I, Jissmon Joseph, acknowledge that I have read and understood all the terms and conditions mentioned above. I make this promise with a pure heart and genuine intentions. I commit to being honest, loving, and remaining the same person you care about today. This contract represents my dedication to our friendship and relationship, and I will honor these promises every single day.
                <br><br>
                <span class="heart">â™¥</span> <em>"You are not just my girlfriend, you are my best friend, my confidant, and my greatest blessing."</em> <span class="heart">â™¥</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="signature-section">
                <div class="signature-row">
                    <div class="signature-box">
                        <div class="signature-line"></div>
                        <div class="signature-text">Jissmon Joseph<br>(Your Best Friend Forever)</div>
                        <div class="thumb-impression"></div>
                        <div class="signature-text" style="margin-top: 5px;">Thumb Impression</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="signature-box">
                        <div class="signature-line"></div>
                        <div class="signature-text"><strong>Jyoti Kush</strong><br>(My Heart & Soul)</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="date-section">
                 <span class="date-line" style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; color: #8B4513;">November 15, 2024</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>